parameters:
\SE[2]Um, is it... over? \SE[20]I mean, it's not exactly a cool
memory, so it's embarrassing to look at it again...

\SE[12]Um, is this... a... big pinch...!? \SE[24]I can't handle
this on my own! Someone, help meee!!

\SE\SE[15]So you came to help me...!! \!\SE[15]As expected, Miss
is reliable!!

\SE[92]You're telling me to quit being a Miss, right?
\SE[2]...And what do you mean by help? I was just suddenly thrown
into this without any explanation...
\SE[90]...I see. I don't really understand, but I got it.

\SE[4]I need a few more people. \!\SE[3]Can't we call someone
using the same method?

\SE[14]Oh, the same method... It's worth a try! Let's give it a
shot...!!
\SE[4]W-What...!? I ended up in a strange place...!

\SE\SE[0]Oh... the world is full of strange things, isn't it?
\!\SE[0]It's becoming difficult to be surprised.

\SE[14]Oh, two reliable people have arrived! \!\SE[0]With this,
our fighting force should be more than enough, don't you think?

\SE[90]Well, it's not bad but... \SE[3]I'm a little concerned
that you're leaning too much towards attack. \SE[2]Can't you
balance it out a bit more with defense?

\SE[13]Hmm... you have a point there... \!\SE[1]Then, I'll ask
you two to go back.

\SE[2]Oh, it worked out well. You're doing great. Let's try it
again. \!\SE[24]Someone, help meee!!
\SE[75] (...Was there really a need to send them back?)

\SE\SE[15]Ah, isn't this a good combination!? Ryan-san for
endurance and Rebecca-san for attack...!! \SE[15]With this, I
believe we can meet your request!

\SE[3]I'm listening to the story! I don't really understand, but
I just have to fight, right? \SE[10]Leave it to me! I'll
definitely be useful!!

\SE[47]Hey, stop getting carried away. \SE[39]You're just going
to mess up because you're too excited. [2]Just like last time...

\SE[29]Why are you always like this...!! \!\SE[12]You're weaker
than me, yet you act all high and mighty giving orders!! \.Isn't
it about time you start trusting me!?

\SE[74]... Let's stop these two. \SE[58] I'm not good at
mediation. Me.
\SE[9]No way...!! \.It's such a good opportunity to show off...!!

\SE\SE[24]I'm starting to get the hang of it. Let's go for one
more shot. \SE[24]Someone, help me!!

\SE[10]It seems like you're saying 'It's no good without me. You
should rely on me' right?\SE[1]

\SE[2]Huh? It's quite unbalanced, isn't it? \SE[0]I feel like
this might work!

\SE[2]Yes, let's go with this. \!\SE[3]...The introduction has
become too long.

\SE[22]You made me wait for quite a while! \!\SE[19]Now, let's
go!
